Description: looplook is a versatile R package for target assignment and functional
    annotation of chromatin interactions. It leverages customizable genomic feature
    integration, expression-aware refinement, and connected components clustering
    to prioritize biologically relevant chromatin interactions. The package also
    provides flexible tools for multi-omics data integration, functional annotation,
    and data visualization.
